               <msContents>
                  <summary>The Ms. contains the following texts:
 I) Dǝrsāna kidāna mǝḥrat
                     “Homily for the Covenant of Mercy” (fols. 3ra-39vb)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa kidāna
                     mǝḥrat “Book of the Covenant of Mercy” (fols. 15rb-18vb)
 I-2) Maṣḥafa
                     lǝdäta la-Māryām “Book of the Nativity of Mary” (fols. 18vb-31rb), including:
                     Story of St Anna (fol. 23rb), engagement of St Mary with Joseph (fol. 25rb),
                     conception of St Mary (fols. 28rb) (cp. M. CHAINE (ed., tr.), Apocrypha de
                     Beata Maria Virgine, Romae 1909 (CSCO 39, 40 [SAe 22, 23]), 3-19 (text) = 3-16
                     (tr.))
 I-3) Covenant of Mercy (fols. 31rb-39vb) (V. ARRAS (ed., tr.), De
                     transitu Mariae apocrypha aethiopice, II, Louvain 1974 (CSCO 351, 352 [SAe 68,
                     69]), 73-85 (text) = 56-67 (tr.))
 II) Miracles of the Covenant of Mary in
                     the land of Ethiopia (fols. 39vb- 57va) (C. CONTI ROSSINI, "Il convent di Tsana
                     in Abissinia e le sue laudi alla Vergine: Nota di Carlo Conti Rossini,
                     presentation dal Socio Ignazio Guidi", RRALm ser. 5, 19, 1910, 581-621).
                     III) Malkǝʾa kidāna mǝḥrat “Image of the Covenant of Mercy” (57vb-63vb) (cp.
                     Malkǝʾa gubaʾe, ʾAśmära 1974 E.C., 112-122), incomplete.</summary>
